System Overview:
Phase 1 :
1. NGOs will list the sub-funds dedicated to specific cause.
2. Each sub-fund will list the estimated fund required.
3.Doner will donate to for perticular cause using blockchain wallet.
4.Transaction records will be generated. 
5.Records should show:
   a. Amount of money transfered, 
   b. Name of donor and organization
   c. Donor's balance after transaction
   d. Total collection of the organization after transaction.
   e. Total collection for the perticular cause
 6.Funds,Sub-Funds, Wallets are updated accordingly.


Phase -2

1 Donor  can also track the fund disbursement
2. Disbursement will also record the details of local partners where fund got disbursed.
